---++GlueLocation Attributes
!GlueLocation entity provides details of the VO softwares (e.g. location, version) that have been installed as well as execution environments to jobs.

dn: !GlueLocationLocalID=ENV_NAME,GlueSubClusterUniqueID=CE_FQDN,GlueClusterUniqueID=CE_FQDN,mds-vo-name=local,o=grid 

*NOTES*:
   1. We currently fill in OSG_SITE_READ, OSG_SITE_WRITE and OSG_GRID location information statically
   1. An OSG-GIP provider named &quot;osg-info-software-provider&quot; puts in location information about all software defined in $OSG_APP/etc/grid3-location.txt.

|  *Attributes*  |  *Static/Dynamic*  |  *Requires Extra Admin Intervention*  |  *Usage form*  |  *Believe value is Correct(Y/N/?)*  |  *Comments*  | *Critical?* | 
| !GlueChunkKey | S | N | !GlueClusterUniqueID=... | Y | This associates cluster within a subcluster | A | 
| !GlueLocationName | S/D | N | ENV or SW Name | Y | Both Static and Dynamic. | A |
| !GlueLocationLocalID | S/D | N | ENV or SW Name | Y | &quot; | A |
| !GlueLocationVersion | S/D | N | Version Number | Y | Undefined for OSG_SITE_READ, OSG_SITE_WRITE and OSG_GRID | A |
| !GlueLocationPath | S/D | N | Path to Env variable or SW | Y | Absolute Paths | A |
| !GlueSchemaVersionMajor | S | N | 1 | Y | | A |
| !GlueSchemaVersionMinor | S | N | 2 | Y | | A |

